    {
      "id": "comm-details",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 520,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "AgentMessage Protocol:\n  content · sender_id · sender_did · message_type · message_id\n  conversation_id · in_reply_to · metadata · timestamp\n\nSync:   POST /webhook/sync   →  immediate JSON response\nAsync:  POST /webhook        →  queued, poll for response\nRoutes to framework: LangChain | LangGraph | CrewAI | PydanticAI | Custom",
