      "type": "text",
      "x": 820,
      "y": 552,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "Request ────→ HTTP 402 ────→ Auto-pay USDC ────→ Retry with proof\n\nX402PaymentProcessor    intercepts 402, signs payment, retries\nEthAccountSigner        wallet derived from agent seed\nFlask Middleware         gates /webhook and /webhook/sync routes",
